query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS channel_inventory (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  productId INT NOT NULL,
  sku VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  channel ENUM('shipstation', 'woocommerce', 'amazon', 'tiktok', 'ebay') NOT NULL,
  warehouseId VARCHAR(100),
  warehouseName VARCHAR(255),
  availableQty INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  buffer INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  zeroStockThreshold INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  manualOverride INT,
  lastSyncAt TIMESTAMP,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX product_idx (productId),
  INDEX sku_idx (sku),
  INDEX channel_idx (channel),
  UNIQUE KEY unique_product_channel_warehouse (productId, channel, warehouseId)
)
